snippet.textDisplay:
This is such a gorgeous piece! I wish I understood Urdu better to appreciate the lyrics better. Atif has such a beautiful folk voice and the rhythm is soothing and uplifting at the same time. Music truly bridges all boundaries and gaps. It knows only one language irrespective of boundaries, faith, race, and sex! 

If someone could help me with the lyrics and translation, it'd be real nice! 

Love from Singapore! <3
